import React, { useState } from 'react'
import {Card, Collapse, Navbar, NavbarToggler, NavbarBrand, Nav, NavItem, NavLink} from 'reactstrap'






const LogIn = () => {

    const [collapsed, setCollapesed] = useState(true);

    const toggleNavbar = () => setCollapesed(!collapsed)

    return(

        <>
        <Navbar color>
            <NavbarBrand>Wave Suggester</NavbarBrand>
            <NavbarToggler onClick={toggleNavbar} className="mr-2" />
            <Collapse isOpen={!collapsed} navbar>
                <Nav navbar>
                    <NavItem>
                        <NavLink>About</NavLink>
                    </NavItem>
                    <NavItem>
                        <NavLink>Contact</NavLink>
                    </NavItem>
                </Nav>
            </Collapse>
        </Navbar>
        <Card>
    
        </Card>
    
    
        </>
    


    )
  
  

}



export default LogIn
